            "text": "<p>At Paez, simplicity is key and what takes us far. We were able to transform the iconic espadrille into a fashion trend. With comfort and creativity, we connected the world with our purpose. Now, we’re aiming for new heights. New product categories, new prints, and new shades to become your wardrobe essential for every occasion.</p>",
