          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Thinking of the SS23 collection, we wanted to make a statement. It’s possible to align relaxation and quality without compromising on style. We work every day to provide unique experiences and a laid-back mindset to everyone who walks around in their favourite Paez design. It’s time to be free, to take new chances, to challenge ourselves to become our best and most inspiring versions.<br/><br/>We’re blossoming not only in new designs, like the Mary Janes, but also in returning ones, like the Sandals, Mules, and Mocs while delivering the best version of our espadrille collections.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
